                },
                {
                    "video_time": 133.445842,
                    "list": "[\"He's starting to really lose that embodiment of the rhythm.\", \"He's really falling off the rhythm and moving at a significantly slower pace.\", 'His upper body is continuing to move in sort of a free motion above him.', 'He might want to tighten up that upper body and be more clear and direct in his movements.']",
                    "expert_uid": "mg5x5a",
                    "video_name": "upenn_0706_Dance_4_3"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 142.886016,
                    "list": "['make sure he adds a little more hip movement', 'a little more variety with the arms', 'just keeping the beat and the timing is something he could work on']",
