                    "expert_uid": "tja8o9",
                    "video_name": "upenn_0721_Piano_1_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 85.603002,
                    "list": "[\"This line that they're playing is losing a lot of clarity because of their fingers being so far off the keyboard. They should try to keep it as close as possible so when it's clear then it'll be easier to listen to.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "tja8o9",
                    "video_name": "upenn_0721_Piano_1_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 105.521112,
                    "list": "['The pianist is losing a little bit of clarity here', \"It's just a little bit too fast for them\", 'They should try to slow it down a bit']",
                    "expert_uid": "tja8o9",
                    "video_name": "upenn_0721_Piano_1_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 118.947086,
                    "list": "[\"make sure that they're very efficient with their hands\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "tja8o9",
                    "video_name": "upenn_0721_Piano_1_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 131.554998,
                    "list": "['This ascending line could use a little bit more coordination and accuracy.', \"They're coming off really high with their fingers and their hands, which is not helping them.\", 'They should try to make sure that they do this very slowly and really see if they can minimize as much motion.']",
                    "expert_uid": "tja8o9",
                    "video_name": "upenn_0721_Piano_1_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 166.414711,
                    "list": "['The pianist should check with the metronome', \"It feels like it's much faster than how they started\", 'It starts to feel a bit hectic and out of control.']",
