                    "video_name": "upenn_0721_Piano_1_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 496.604433,
                    "list": "['The pianist should try to play this section with a metronome.', \"It's often rushing and the rhythms start to feel compressed, like there's not a lot of room between them.\"]",
