                    "video_name": "upenn_0721_Piano_1_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 545.389192,
                    "list": "['The pianist could have pasted this crescendo a little bit more gradually, starting softer, and then a little bit more, and then a little bit more, and then a little bit more, just so that it feels like it has more musical sense.']",
