                    "video_name": "upenn_0721_Piano_1_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 781.436711,
                    "list": "['The left hand notes are starting to fall apart a bit.', \"This whole time they've been playing with flat fingers which results in more motion and more fatigue.\", 'They would be able to play consistently more even if they used their fingertips.']",
