                },
                {
                    "video_time": 13.866686,
                    "list": "[\"He's kind of upright.\", 'In this drill, my recommendation is the shooter drop his hips, bend his knees and step one, two to meet this pass to get more lift and elevation and make it more game-like.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 14.447789,
                    "list": "[\"He's not going to meet it with what I call a one-two step.\", 'So you got to meet your pass in any of those situations.', \"But let's extend them more out to meet the pass.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 15.035903,
                    "list": "[\"he catches it, there's like a hesitation or a pause here\", \"So we've got to be quicker, stepping in and meeting the pass\", \"we've got to catch and shoot a little bit quicker here\", 'his feet are really close together', 'My recommendation is to really step in with that left foot, pull the right foot up and then elevate', \"Here it's just a little bit too slow\"]",
