                {
                    "video_time": 15.694772,
                    "list": "['having his right hand rely flat on the side, using it as just a placeholder in keeping the ball in the correct alignment']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 15.712996,
                    "list": "['I would love for him to jump up vertically to go up straight.', 'Here the elbows have a tendency to kind of pop out a little bit.', \"Let's bring these elbows in under the basketball.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 16.10879,
                    "list": "['You see that that arm it kind of follow throughs a little bit across his body instead of straight on.', \"Let's get this left elbow of the non shooting arm parallel to the floor.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 20.904987,
                    "list": "[\"The player's body momentum is bringing him further away from the basket after the release, which does not allow the ball to continue its gain of proper arc, accuracy, and rotation.\", 'Develop the proper angle of dropping inside the rim.']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 20.904987,
                    "list": "[\"The player's body momentum is bringing him further away from the basket after the release, which does not allow the ball to continue its gain of proper arc, accuracy, and rotation.\", 'Develop the proper angle of dropping inside the rim.']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 26.608836,
                    "list": "['On the release, he kind of short arms his follow through a little bit.', \"It's a little bit down too low. Let's get that follow through up.\", 'He also jerks back that non-shooting hand as well. You can see that in the image here.', \"Let's square these shoulders and hip up.\", \"It looks like he turns that right leg in a little bit. Let's get our whole body squared in the basket.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 31.159414,
                    "list": "[\"Again, let's square our hips to the basket.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 31.28532,
                    "list": "['his elbow is slightly above the level of his eyes']",
                    "expert_uid": "bsgo5b",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 36.100635,
                    "list": "['I really would love to see more elevation in the release of the ball at the height of his jump.', 'Can he jump higher? I think so.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 39.892789,
                    "list": "['Waiting to meet the pass', 'Bend our knees', 'Drop our hips', 'Get our feet apart', 'Step into the pass']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 40.524838,
                    "list": "[\"It's going to take him a while to get it off. Therefore he's going to be defended.\", \"Why don't we step this left foot aggressively, bring the right leg in aggressively when you catch it.\", 'Just little footwork, just little small step.', 'He holds it here a little bit too long.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_4"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 41.125373,
                    "list": "['He does bend his knees here a little bit.', \"The shooting elbow looks like it's a little bit out. Let's bring that elbow in under the ball.\", \"He's bringing the ball really a little bit back behind his head. You'd like to shoot it from the forehead.\"]",
