                    "video_name": "georgiatech_bike_06_6"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 12.763319,
                    "list": "['she went ahead and pulled back the derailleur here just to release the tension on that chain allowing a better easy installation', 'by putting the derailleur back you allow the cassette to be easily placed between the chain and the derailleur itself']",
                    "expert_uid": "zchsw0",
                    "video_name": "georgiatech_bike_06_6"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 18.593325,
                    "list": "['the system that the mechanic used to orient the wheel and the chain and then pull the derailleur back so that all falls into place was done quite well.']",
                    "expert_uid": "49plbb",
                    "video_name": "georgiatech_bike_06_6"
                },
