                    "video_time": 37.891966,
                    "list": "['seat the axle into the dropouts more securely', 'ensure proper alignment of the axle and dropouts']",
                    "expert_uid": "7ygad1",
                    "video_name": "georgiatech_bike_06_6"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 45.938026,
                    "list": "[\"This process sometimes can be done easier if the bike's on the ground and then you have gravity on your side, the weight of the frame holding it all the way in the dropout. So that would be my suggestion.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "49plbb",
                    "video_name": "georgiatech_bike_06_6"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 46.311377,
