                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-16-23_01_30"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 17.911679,
                    "list": "['Improvements the player can make to become more efficient on his attempt is by starting out using the proper footwork', 'stepping with his left foot first and having his right foot come down second going into his release', 'the player can jump on two feet at the same time allowing himself to be more on balance going in to his release.']",
