                    "video_time": 52.669712,
                    "list": "['he was able to do that with a right foot on a foothold', 'the flagging foot is mainly there in this instance for good body control', \"his arms are in a straight position so that he's maintaining as much energy in his arms and he's relying on his legs to hold onto most of his body weight\"]",
