                },
                {
                    "video_time": 53.918304,
                    "list": "['he readjust his right hand to this pinch', 'his foot is actually kind of engaged with the wall', \"his whole body's kind of twisting into the side\", 'he can brace his chest against his forearm', 'his whole torso is kind of swapping around and kind of digging into his torso', 'puts your shoulder at a more advantageous position', 'rest it against your body and lean into it', 'provides a little bit of counterforce and just kind of stabilizes the whole position', 'makes a little bit of a stronger position to be in']",
