                },
                {
                    "video_time": 4.770665,
                    "list": "['However, on this attempt, the shooter, he put a lot of side spin on the ball. So when it hit the backboard, it spun and we end up missing it long to the left side of the rim.']",
                    "expert_uid": "bsgo5b",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_3"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 8.957774,
                    "list": "['A slight adjustment we will want to make to improve on creating more security and protection for the offensive player.', 'As we look on the right frame is to bring his ball placement position a little bit higher towards his shoulder area.', 'Creating a closer opportunity for the ball to hit our targeted area.', 'And bringing it away from opposing defenders being able to attempt to steal, take, or strip the ball.']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_3"
                },
