                    "video_time": 36.913724,
                    "list": "['He did a good job staying on the beat.', 'He got a little bit off at the end but he definitely tried his best to stay on with the timing.', 'So really nice bend.', 'Really good job holding his balance and being able to do the kicks right after.']",
