            "tips_for_improvement": [
                {
                    "video_time": 6.956879,
                    "list": "['She should start closer to the baseline for maximum extension and to mimic in-game situations.']",
                    "expert_uid": "500w0s",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 6.959589,
                    "list": "['Would like to see a little better footwork here with the right left foot takeoff.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 7.090211,
                    "list": "['if she could replicate that in the step before']",
                    "expert_uid": "500w0s",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 7.425977,
                    "list": "['We will want to point her shoulders towards the sideline. Her shoulders are pointed towards the baseline right now, giving her a less likely chance for the ball to have a crucial spin towards the backboard to complete a successful finish.']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 7.660589,
                    "list": "['For a reverse layup, her body needs to be shifted towards the sideline', 'Her body placement facing the baseline will make it more difficult to shield a defender']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 7.790204,
                    "list": "['She should work on jumping off one foot instead of two for better lift and extension on the layup.', 'On the left side, she needs to focus on proper technique for laying up the ball instead of pushing it.']",
                    "expert_uid": "500w0s",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 7.983619,
                    "list": "['Another minor adjustment we can make for this player to improve her finishing ability on her reverse layups. As we can notice on the left frame, we see that her hand is pushing the ball forward. We will want to rotate her hand towards the right to give the ball a slight spin to be able to hit our located target, which is on the right corner of the box on the backboard.']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 8.042737,
                    "list": "['Tilt the hand towards the right side to give the ball more spin and increase the chance of scoring']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 8.056867,
                    "list": "['placement on the backboard needs improvement', 'advanced spin and a good angle are needed to get the ball in']",
                    "expert_uid": "500w0s",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 8.356863,
                    "list": "['the ball kind of just careens off the backboard. So initially this is signaling more of a beginner.']",
                    "expert_uid": "500w0s",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 8.770094,
                    "list": "[\"Understanding the concept of what she's attempting to do first and foremost\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "ec8x25",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 11.768079,
                    "list": "['Shot would be improved with better footwork here.', 'She kind of shuffles her feet instead of taking maybe a one, two step, big steps to the basket.', 'We kind of shuffled her feet there in this camera view.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 12.529561,
                    "list": "['maybe a little bit more take off on one foot', 'maybe pull this right knee up']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 15.458577,
                    "list": "[\"we'd love to see a big one-two step to gather momentum\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 16.376831,
                    "list": "['Take a little bit off when hitting the backboard.', \"Want the ball to hit the backboard as it's going down, not as it's going up.\", 'Follow the fundamentals.']",
                    "expert_uid": "ec8x25",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 19.992514,
                    "list": "['No dribbling', 'No rhythm', 'Lack of fluency']",
                    "expert_uid": "ec8x25",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 20.170941,
                    "list": "[\"She's a beginner and she's more so throwing it off the backboard.\", \"There's no follow through in the hand either.\", \"She's kind of just like shot putting it and that's where we see the ball is just going off the backboard.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "500w0s",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 24.186423,
                    "list": "['Again, this drill and her form and technique would be much improved if she would do a right-left take-off.', 'Little shuffling of the feet, not as balanced maybe in terms of getting that shot off.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 24.321487,
                    "list": "[\"The angle she's also taking is super flat.\", 'She wants to be able to come down from her high ankle to give herself a better chance at making this layup.', \"And also just understanding if you're going to come off two feet, be able to have that flexion and try to release it at the peak of your jump.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "ec8x25",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 28.905291,
                    "list": "['shuffling of the feet', 'going off two feet', 'need to do left right step', 'push up with right knee']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 29.489004,
                    "list": "[\"The player's hand on the left side of the frame is tilting a little bit towards the right\", 'Pushing the ball towards the back of the rim, not giving it a chance to be higher above the rim', 'Pushing the ball on the outer side of the rim will just allow it to come right back towards you', \"If the offensive player's hand tilted a little bit more towards the right and gave the ball a higher chance, we'll have a better opportunity of hitting our target area and going through the net for a successful finish.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 34.034732,
                    "list": "['she was a little bit more to the right', 'the ball needs to be angled more so it hits the square and has a chance to go in']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 34.119909,
                    "list": "['Here is way too low.', \"She's not giving herself an opportunity to get close to making the leg up.\", \"making sure you're hitting the backboard high and soft in order to be able to.\", \"I'll give yourself a better chance at making the layout.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "ec8x25",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_02-24-23_01_36"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 42.891759,
                    "list": "['Her posture is going straight forward. She has no angle at coming in to make that layup.', 'Neither does she have any English on the spin and this is going to make it even tougher almost like a zero chance at making it.']",
