                    "video_name": "uniandes_dance_002_3"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 26.07059,
                    "list": "[\"his toe should also move off the floor when he's stepping on his left foot\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "a44vde",
                    "video_name": "uniandes_dance_002_3"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 31.193899,
                    "list": "['He does a little better at picking up his feet, but just not as much.', 'I would definitely say maybe bend those knees a little bit more and really get the hips into the movement going side to side.', 'They should be also pushing side to side as well.']",
                    "expert_uid": "a44vde",
                    "video_name": "uniandes_dance_002_3"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 37.393978,
                    "list": "[\"Pick those feet up just a little bit more because they're just kind of dragging and it brings the energy down to the floor.\"]",
