                },
                {
                    "video_time": 119.403728,
                    "list": "['To improve these step twists, encourage them to send their hips back more and pli\u00e9 or bend their legs even more', 'Also, work on the balls of the foot to help with range of motion', 'This would improve the dance by creating more accuracy and articulation in the knees']",
