                    "video_name": "upenn_0713_Dance_5_6"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 181.393955,
                    "list": "[\"To improve this section of the choreography, I would encourage the dancer to have more strength and power in their arms, which I've previously talked about, that would help the lines and the dimension and allow them to be able to take up more space.\"]",
