                    "list": "['The dancer is clearly lacking stamina.', \"Her movement isn't nearly as dynamic as it was at the beginning of this performance.\", \"She's running out of energy.\", \"She's struggling with a lot of different transitional steps.\", 'She appears a little bit confused, not making any clear shapes with the body.', 'Overall, she is just lacking the energy she had prior.']",
