                    "list": "['Here you have the climber brushing the holds.', 'A really good tactic for just the extra edge in climbing.', 'You want to hedge your bets on every attempt.', 'It also allows us to get a really good look at the top of this hold.', 'It looks pretty good and I can understand why climbers are going to the top of this hold.', 'Often times climbers will brush to clean the hold and regain a bit of friction on the hold but also to investigate and study the hold.', 'For some reason the brush allows us to see the hold and experience the hold in a way that can be helpful and advantageous to the climber.']",
