                },
                {
                    "video_time": 177.713004,
                    "list": "['However, you can see that the knife is slightly dull.', \"There's resistance trying to cut through some of those tomatoes.\", 'Sharpening the knife would improve the ability to easily cut through those tomatoes.']",
                    "expert_uid": "d2vast",
                    "video_name": "sfu_cooking_008_1"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 240.298987,
                    "list": "['Whisking should be done properly from a bottom to top circular motion to incorporate air into the mixture and create a fluffy egg mixture.']",
                    "expert_uid": "bk8szu",
                    "video_name": "sfu_cooking_008_1"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 240.517172,
                    "list": "['Other types of tools you could use would be a fork or a wire whisk.', 'The goal here is that you thoroughly mix the eggs so that you achieve a homogeneous mixture without any streaks of white and yolk separate from the mixture.']",
                    "expert_uid": "d2vast",
                    "video_name": "sfu_cooking_008_1"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 307.250666,
                    "list": "['the oil is going to be a little less viscous']",
