                    "list": "[\"The player's first touch should move the ball forwards into the space for a more successful pass.\", 'Turning and moving through the ball on contact is important instead of just redirecting the ball.', 'Adjustment in footwork is needed during controlling touch.', 'The feet should not be too close together and the legs should have some knee bend for better pass execution.']",
