                {
                    "video_time": 34.304714,
                    "list": "[\"So his position behind the ball probably accordingly even though like he didn't really have to move to adjust to get behind this pass\", 'Ball contact seems fine.', \"It's just that he's not leaning at all\", \"So he's like he's very upright in this extra in this clip.\", \"So he's not actually moving in the direction To be able to bring the ball in the direction that he kind of wants to go\", \"So he's not going to generate any momentum or force in that direction\", \"It's all going to be based off of his first touch.\", 'So the speed of this action is going to look very slow then', \"Compared to if he's already leaning and go in in that direction\"]",
