                    "list": "['Although this pass with the left foot reaches its intended target, it travels slowly in little pace.', 'To improve the weight of the pass, we want to see the player punch through the line of the intended direction of the pass with his foot locked in the same position from approaching the ball to striking the ball to through the ball, which is toe down.', 'Ankle locked using the outer top part of the foot or the dorsal surface of the foot', 'Get the knee positioned correctly close or over the ball', 'This then allows for that flexibility and freedom for the lower part of the leg to strike through the ball', 'Return the foot to a position which will then allow for better movement after the pass.']",
