                {
                    "video_time": 9.721749,
                    "list": "['He brings the ball down really low before transitioning to the left side.', 'In this drill, ideally the execution involves getting the ball off the rim or out of the net by keeping your arms up high.', \"He drops the ball which is not ideal in a game situation since it can be easily stripped away if you're not being aggressive.\"]",
