                    "list": "['Not allow the ball to drop down down to our waist level']",
                    "expert_uid": "bsgo5b",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 10.307507,
                    "list": "['You want to keep it up here. You want to make yourself as big and tall as possible.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 10.354638,
                    "list": "['have his ball placement position higher above his shoulders to allow more ball control and security going into the finish', 'allowing a quicker release towards our target area by bringing the ball in a closer gap towards the target']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 10.354638,
                    "list": "['benefit the player to have his body placement position lower in the athletic stance']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 10.639672,
                    "list": "['his knee is pretty low and not near his waist level', 'we need to get that knee up higher on the jump so we can explode and jump higher', 'so we can release the ball at his highest point']",
                    "expert_uid": "bsgo5b",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 10.82165,
                    "list": "['stepped on that right', 'pull that left leg and knee up high', 'get some power here from the legs']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 11.026501,
                    "list": "['The player did not do a great job of getting his follow-through', 'The player did not go towards the direction of the basket', 'The player allowed the ball to travel above the rim with too much power and force', 'The player did not give the ball an opportunity to drop in the rim']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 15.101204,
                    "list": "[\"some improvement the player can make to become more efficient on his layup attempts is to jump with full maximum effort, allowing his body's momentum to carry him higher and closer towards the target area.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 15.224249,
                    "list": "['His score is indicative of him not powering it up more.', \"Really lift, if you're gonna go off two feet, really power yourself up and get up off the ground.\", 'He needs to go with a higher level of intensity and urgency.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 16.67141,
                    "list": "['Starting body placement position lower in the athletic stance', \"Carrying body's momentum towards the left side of the rim\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 16.67141,
                    "list": "['We want the player to bring his ball placement positioned higher above his shoulders to allow more ball control and security going into the finish', 'Releasing the ball more accurately towards our target area and preventing opposing defenders in the game light scenario from stripping, taking or stealing the ball from the offensive player']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 16.916273,
                    "list": "['Here you start to see a little pulling of the left knee. I really feel like it could be more.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 17.493889,
                    "list": "[\"Let's lift\", \"Let's use our legs and hips more\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 17.603117,
                    "list": "['The placement of the ball on the backboard should be higher, above the square.', 'More side spin is needed on the ball to ensure it spins off the backboard and into the basket.', 'The ball should be placed slightly above the top portion of the square for better results.']",
                    "expert_uid": "bsgo5b",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 17.804732,
                    "list": "['our players inability to get enough lift off the ground', 'The ball did not gain enough arc and accuracy to get above the rim']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 19.275134,
                    "list": "['I really want him to really push off this left foot and draw that right hip up.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 19.440655,
                    "list": "[\"He's a little low in the release here. He could definitely be higher.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "500w0s",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 19.723529,
                    "list": "['Kind of short arms adhere. Would love to see it more extended.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 21.213861,
                    "list": "['He lets the ball drop down', 'His feet are a little close together', \"We'd love to see a big step through with that right foot\", 'Pull that left leg up']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 23.887341,
                    "list": "[\"Let's get more legs here\", \"Let's get more power and lift and elevation\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 26.393145,
                    "list": "['be aggressive', 'move with big steps instead of little ones']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 31.626987,
                    "list": "[\"Let's square this left shoulder so we're shooting facing the basket.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 33.006581,
                    "list": "[\"I would just love to see more, just a bigger step through with like that's more aggressive, takes up more space, gets him there a little bit quicker.\", \"Let's get that ball up. Let's keep it up here chest shoulder level.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 34.99015,
                    "list": "[\"he didn't really extend as high as he should have or get as much lift as he should have\", 'he was pretty sloppy with the ball placement', 'he missed a lot of shots']",
                    "expert_uid": "500w0s",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_2"
                }
            ]
        },
