                },
                {
                    "video_time": 4.710661,
                    "list": "[\"Ideally in this drill, the Mike and drill, you'd love to see him get that rebound and then step through with the right foot and really pull this left knee up.\", \"he's just choosing to kind of slide from side to side.\", 'We would just love to see more push off and aggression here.', \"Getting ready to shoot here, we'd love that guide hand, that right hand to stay a little bit longer on the ball.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-16-23_01_28"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 4.87058,
                    "list": "[\"Here's the guide hand, you know, we'd love for it to be a little bit higher, maybe to take it up and then you keep it up there a little higher, maybe right in here. If there was like a, you know, a defender coming over, you want that arm bar to protect the ball.\", \"Here a better take off here, he's got his feet spread apart, which is fine. You know, I would love to see, ideally the footwork for this is off the right foot and pull that left knee up, but if he's going to power it up off two feet, you know, let's really get some lift and aggression here.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-16-23_01_28"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 7.209,
                    "list": "['bringing his ball placement position higher above his shoulder', 'allowing more space from opposing defenders', 'creating more ball control and security on the finish']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-16-23_01_28"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 7.209,
                    "list": "['bringing his ball placement position higher above his shoulder', 'allowing more space from opposing defenders', 'creating more ball control and security on the finish']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
