                },
                {
                    "video_time": 7.250719,
                    "list": "['Ideally you want to get the ball out of the net and keep it up high.', 'He drops it down really low here.', 'When you bring it down here, you make yourself smaller and more vulnerable.', \"If he chooses to go off two feet, let's really use these two legs to really push ourselves up off the ground.\"]",
