                    "list": "['Here he has increased the heat to a relatively high flame.', 'A better way to do this would be to start simmering the milk using a medium heat.', 'Bring it up to a high simmer where you see just tiny little bubbles starting.', 'Then bring the heat down to a simmer to steep the tea leaves rather than boiling them.']",
