                    "list": "['Improvements that can help the player become more efficient on his attempts is stepping with the proper footwork.', \"We want the player to step and jump with his left foot, allowing his body's momentum to carry him closer towards the right side of the rim.\", 'Preventing opposing defenders in the game-light scenario having easy access of blocking and contesting the player shot.']",
