                    "list": "[\"Be careful with the amount of side spin on the ball when it's inside the square.\", 'Place the ball outside of the square to avoid spinning off the backboard.', 'Avoid putting too much spin on the ball to prevent it from spinning off the right side of the rim.', 'Avoid the toilet bowl effect by not catching the inside of the right portion of the rim.', 'Try to prevent the ball from spinning around the rim.']",
