                    "list": "['the climber was able to get his left hand onto the next hand hold', 'he was able to do that mainly from this left heel hook', 'the climber has now been able to do a lot of moves with the use of this left heel hook', 'the main take away from a good heel hook is that it helps to bring your hip up and closer into the wall', 'it helps to relieve the amount of energy you might need to use for your upper body', 'it allows your lower body to do the main pulling force', 'especially as can be seen in this effort right here']",
