                {
                    "video_time": 12.534031,
                    "list": "['And it did not seem like any bodyweight transfer from one foot to the other happened before committing to that next handhold.', 'this is something I would discourage for any future attempts', 'I would always encourage that the climber tries to transfer his bodyweight from one foot to the next, or find a higher foot position before committing to a higher handhold.']",
