                {
                    "video_time": 189.595104,
                    "list": "['Instead of that, it is more effective to use a large circular motion with the entire swab.', \"So using your entire wrist or arm, you want to keep that swab in contact with the inner lining of your nare for the entire time that you're swabbing.\", 'That way you get more of a sample on that swab to use for your test.']",
