                {
                    "video_time": 191.666919,
                    "list": "['My worry with him pinching his nose, I can see from behind he has the swab inside the nostril.', \"You don't wanna have your nose pinched while taking the test.\", \"That could also cause damage like nosebleeds and things like that when you don't have that canal open.\", 'You wanna be able to swab your nares in a nice circular motion and slowly about five times.']",
