            "tips_for_improvement": [
                {
                    "video_time": 2.212958,
                    "list": "['improvements the player can make to become quicker, more explosive, and balanced on his initial drive going towards the rim is getting his body placement position lower in the athletic stance.']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 2.212958,
                    "list": "['improvements the player can make to become quicker, more explosive, and balanced on his initial drive going towards the rim is getting his body placement position lower in the athletic stance.']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 2.54899,
                    "list": "[\"In order to reach the highest point of our jump, we have to make sure that when we jump that we lift the right knee up to our waist level as we're exploding up into the air from the ground.\", \"By not getting his knee up to his waist level as he's exploding off of the ground off his left foot with the jump from the ground up into the air, this means that he is not reaching the highest point of his jump.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "bsgo5b",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 2.605837,
                    "list": "['his push off is just not as aggressive as you would like it to be.', 'he could really push up off hard and really pull that right hip up more aggressively to get more lift and elevation', \"he's really having to take this ball long ways to shoot it\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 8.601451,
                    "list": "['Just lacks the intensity', 'Gotta go hard and be aggressive', 'Would love to see more lift and elevation on the shot']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 8.609762,
                    "list": "['bring his ball placement position higher above his shoulder', 'create more space from opposing defenders', 'create more ball control and security', 'create a closer and quicker gap of releasing the ball towards our target']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 8.609762,
                    "list": "['bring his ball placement position higher above his shoulder', 'create more space from opposing defenders', 'create more ball control and security', 'create a closer and quicker gap of releasing the ball towards our target']",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 8.930599,
                    "list": "['Ideally we would like for his arm to be up a little bit higher.', \"By having his arm up higher, it protects the ball as he's releasing the ball.\", \"So, by having that arm up, the defense would have to make contact with his left arm as he's releasing the ball.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "bsgo5b",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 9.097943,
                    "list": "[\"He doesn't really get off the floor very much.\", 'He would love to see this arm more extended than bent here because he has let the ball go.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 14.10962,
                    "list": "[\"We'd love this dribble to be out in front of you.\", 'Usually I call this a power dribble.', 'Like that one dribble is hard and it gives your body momentum.', 'It helps it to lift off the body.', 'He takes a real passive soft dribble next to him.', 'His feet are really close together.', \"We'd love for the dribble to be more out in front of him and a lot harder and more aggressive.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 14.499584,
                    "list": "['This drill, the layup drill is just if you can cover distance here and have your stride be a lot more lengthen and more aggressive.', \"He's not getting sloppy, you know, and sticking the ball out here with one hand.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 14.803569,
                    "list": "[\"He's not really being efficient with his steps.\", 'He should really be just taking two.', \"His last step is with his left foot and he's going to release off that foot which is right.\", 'He should have the ball on the outside though or at least in the midsection of his body just to keep it away from the defender.']",
                    "expert_uid": "500w0s",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 14.992588,
                    "list": "['Push off hard and aggressive with the left foot', 'Cause the right leg and hip to expand and go up']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 15.18411,
                    "list": "[]",
                    "expert_uid": "6jm95g",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 15.18411,
                    "list": "[]",
