                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 15.296753,
                    "list": "['Would love to see his body more square and shooting more straight on.', 'You can see how his elbow goes way out here.', 'Again, would love to see more lift and elevation and make it more game-like.', \"You've got to get up off the ground to finish around the basket.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 20.518458,
                    "list": "['Definitely should be more efficient with the dribble.', 'He can stretch it out to here.', \"He's being pretty casual with this whole thing.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "500w0s",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 20.995281,
                    "list": "['Steps on the left foot', 'Better stride in terms of getting his feet apart', 'Plant the left foot and turn the body inward', 'Follow the strong right lift of the hip']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 21.276688,
                    "list": "[\"It just barely goes up off the ground. Let's really speed up the movement here.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 21.900839,
                    "list": "['He kind of shoots it over his right shoulder.', 'I love to see him more square here with his body in the picture.', \"He's got a long ways to go when you kind of hook it up there.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 27.278845,
                    "list": "['when you land on this left foot, you also want to use that left foot to be a pivot foot', 'A pivot foot to help square and get your body in this particular movement facing the basket', \"You want to square your shoulders up to this basket that you're shooting at\", \"Let's use that left foot push off pivot to face our body, our hips, our shoulders to the basket\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 27.737988,
                    "list": "['The placement of the ball was too low on the backboard.', 'When placing the ball outside of the square, it needs to be higher near the top portion of the square.']",
                    "expert_uid": "bsgo5b",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 27.815106,
                    "list": "['His right shoulder is not square to the basket.', 'His hips, his knees are all facing that side wall.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 33.713648,
                    "list": "[\"We'd love to see him pick it up a notch\", 'take off the left foot', 'really use it to push up that right knee', \"he's kind of shooting over his right shoulder\", 'See the distance that ball has to travel versus if he came right here with this shot.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 34.075493,
                    "list": "['He missed the one before.', 'Right now I put it at 6 with the kind of lack of effort and more advanced techniques of the drill.']",
                    "expert_uid": "500w0s",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 39.1252,
                    "list": "['He should lengthen his stride and power the dribble out in front of him.', 'He should let the dribble drive his body and help lift his body up.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 39.474145,
                    "list": "['Here, just little steps, maybe even an extra step here. You know, you want to take as few steps as possible. You know, get to the basket and score as quickly as possible.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 39.991256,
                    "list": "[\"Let's square that right shoulder up.\", 'Better job here of squaring the legs and hips.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
                    "video_name": "unc_basketball_03-30-23_02_12"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 59.753701,
