                },
                {
                    "video_time": 38.682399,
                    "list": "[\"He's got his arms straight\", 'His back is kind of rounding', 'His left foot is kind of dangling', 'His hips are so far from the wall', \"He's not really tight and rigid\", 'Practice good tension and always keeping rigidity', 'Ability to put the power to the core', 'Remember where his feet are and avoid relaxing too much']",
