                    "list": "['Recollect and reinitiate the intention of the climb.', 'Not moving too fast, but allowing for the pacing of the boulder to dictate the movement.', 'Maybe even gain some energy back.']",
                    "expert_uid": "2vefmg",
                    "video_name": "uniandes_bouldering_012_35"
                },
                {
                    "video_time": 44.191209,
                    "list": "['with his hands being in a very narrow position, he is at risk of kind of being unbalanced', \"your hips can kind of swing in either direction if they don't have the right footwork\"]",
