                {
                    "video_time": 92.042066,
                    "list": "[\"The player's right foot is placed by the right side of the ball.\", 'We would want them to use the outside of their right foot and be dribbling the ball that way.', 'By doing that, using the outside of their right foot, they will be able to make the scissor action more easily around the ball.', \"By starting their right foot on this side, they're going to make an action which is a little more complex and will put them off balance.\"]",
