                },
                {
                    "video_time": 23.407155,
                    "list": "[\"Here he takes a little extra steps here. He really could get to the basket with one power dribble and one big step on the left foot, but he chooses to take a few extra steps here. It just takes him longer to get there. Let's get the ball up quicker, shoulder level, great job with the eyes and head up.\"]",
                    "expert_uid": "2g7km5",
